examples.en: Writing the book reawakened some bad memories.

examples.en: He hopes the musical will reawaken the public to his talents.

examples.en: Around 1912, the movement, which had grown sluggish, began to reawaken.
examples.ru: Примерно в 1912 году движение, которое стало вялым, начало возрождаться.
